    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span> <strong>Knorr beef stock cube</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>beef stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
