    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reduce the heat to medium-low, add the <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>beef stock</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further</p><p>Meanwhile, roughly chop the <strong>chives</strong></p>",
